---
// SolutionSection.astro — Solução visual first: fluxo adicionar → capa → progresso
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 ml-section">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14 ml-reveal space-y-3">
      <span class="inline-block bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Como funciona</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">
        Do ISBN à estante: <span class="text-amber-600">em segundos.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Adicione qualquer livro e deixe o My Library fazer o resto — capa, metadados, progresso e estatísticas, tudo automático.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Flow animation mockup -->
    <div class="ml-reveal">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-0">

        <!-- Step 1: Buscar livro -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-amber-100 p-5 w-full max-w-xs text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-2xl">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">1. Busque o livro</h3>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 text-left flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
            Cem Anos de Solidão...
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Busca por título, autor ou ISBN</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div class="text-amber-400 text-3xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90 md:mx-2">→</div>

        <!-- Step 2: Capa aparece -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-amber-100 p-5 w-full max-w-xs text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-2xl">✨</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">2. Capa automática</h3>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-400 to-amber-600 w-16 h-24 rounded-md shadow-md flex flex-col items-center justify-end p-1.5 animate-pulse">
              <span class="text-white text-[8px] font-bold text-center leading-tight">Cem Anos de Solidão</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Capa, sinopse e autor em 1 clique</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div class="text-amber-400 text-3xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90 md:mx-2">→</div>

        <!-- Step 3: Marcar progresso -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-amber-100 p-5 w-full max-w-xs text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-2xl">📊</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">3. Progresso marcado</h3>
          <div class="space-y-1.5">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-600">
              <span>Página 184 / 417</span>
              <span class="text-amber-600 font-medium ml-auto">44%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full h-2 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-rose-400 h-full rounded-full" style="width: 44%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Acompanhe a leitura dia a dia</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div class="text-amber-400 text-3xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90 md:mx-2">→</div>

        <!-- Step 4: Celebrar -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-rose-100 p-5 w-full max-w-xs text-center space-y-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-2xl">🎉</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800">4. Celebre!</h3>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-rose-50 border border-amber-100 rounded-lg p-2 space-y-1">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Livro concluído!</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Você leu 31 livros em 2025 🏆</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 text-lg">🥳📖⭐</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Estatísticas atualizadas na hora</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
